1932;;Down Our Street;;British;;Harry Lachman;;Elizabeth Allan, Hugh Williams, Binnie Barnes;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Down_Our_Street;;This drama, set during the Depression, sees the character Charlie Stubbs trying to escape his poverty by becoming a criminal. When this course of action fails he cleans up his act and becomes a cab driver for the woman he loves, Annie Collins. Trouble follows Charlie however when Annie's uncle discovers his past.